{
  "stem": "11179.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It's still named after whoever is the chancellor in Germany.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And several other streets-- it dissipated into several other streets from there on.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But it was the street where all the parades where.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was also probably the widest street in Berlin.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was very, very wide.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was the-- was the Berlin Radio Station.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and I think they also bought [NON-ENGLISH] which is  called the Deutschland Center.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And like I said, they still-- still, now on the spot where our school was, it's a-- it's a television station.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The radio station is still there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So as far as the property, this was always owned by the government since that time.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Enough, I guess, so I realized what was going on very much.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When my father lost his job, I was 10-- 10 years old.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I did pretty well realize it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My father got a notice, six months notice.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he called up the president of the corporation, it was a corporation, who was a good friend of his.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He said, that's ridiculous.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I retract it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Two days later, we get a-- we get a letter from-- you see any kind of-- of a-- especially newspapers, but it was in other factories and so on and other businesses, too, where there were more-- of-- more than eight employees, I remember that.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The eight employees I remember.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They had to have one man form the party in there to be the manager over and above the president of the corporation or chairman of the board.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They had really nothing to say.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That it means nothing-- he has nothing to say, he said.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Under the law of the Third Reich, I have to-- I have to give you notice.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
